Soloing at 39 but dangerous dont do it without SoW or potions<br>
<br>
1: Park the pet somewhere out of aggro of EVERYTHING(fire pet is the best because of the DS)<br>
2: armor your pet with the phantom plate (it does help for sure!)<br>
3:Pull with a light spell(ie Malise or the 50 damage bolt) <br>
4:High tail it back to pet and Sic pet (the HG should not have hit you yet)<br>
5: wait for 3 or 4 good hits then heal pet(HG is around 80-90% by this time)<br>
6: Blaze or bolt I use blaze because its a little quicker ( the HG should be so mad at the pet you wont pull it off)<br>
7: Alternate step 5 and 6 as needed you might not blaze as much as heal pet but it varies from HG to HG<br>
8:after the giant starts to run its a good idea to follow it and be rdy to drop it with a blaze if you see another one coming along adds are death still at 39<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
9: loot (woot 40pp) them med back up to 60m min. at 60mana your odds drop becuase if you fizzle you might not make it hehe<br>
<br>
ENDNOTES: Make sure pet has SoW or Expediance incase you do aggro you can pet kite; also make sure the pet does not die step and take a hit if you need to until pet heal refreshes(with shields up you should be ok for 2 or 3 rounds) well thats it sorry it was so long ! but it works for me at 39 and I still get a little less than 1/2 a blue per kill not the best but hey this is m first char and I want some uber gear LOL. Good luck if your on Saryrn send Ethari a tell I love partnering with other mages only problem is its just not fair for the mobs  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ualitaryoko.showPublicProfile?language=EN>AlitaRyoko</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.geocities.co.jp/HeartLand-Sumire/7069/img/ddani.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 65<br> <font color=#333333>(7/8/02 4:23:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlevels3943.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=51.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.co.jp/HeartLand-Sumire/7069/img/ddani.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: I like EW</span><hr size=1> Hmm.  I was thinking of trying RM with the help of my necromancer friend.  It's ugly crowd control, but it works.  And I've been using the fire pet ever since I hit 39.  So far that pet can hold it's own.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    <p><A HREF=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=174301><img src=http://www.eqsyndicate.com/photos/p_majalita.jpg></p></A>
