ref=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlevels3943.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=51.topic&index=24>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Need suggestions for making $$$ at 39</span><hr size=1> RM is a good place to make cash indeed. But as the HG are overcamped these days (at least on AB), the people are behaving like in kindergarten.<br>
<br>
While in RM I recommend to switch to Cynthia. She isn't great XP at 39 but drops quite some good coin and loot. She's on a ca. 6min timer, has only few HP for a mob her level and no faction hit.  I got up to 4p 6g in coin per kill and various gems and research pages. The gems sell up to 8p at vendors with a charm of 91, so there might be more room for profit. In good times I made about 150-200p in 2 to 3 hours, though it`s been some time as I did Cynthia from 32 to 37 mainly for XP. But I've heard of people who did her til 40 ...<br>
<br>
Yes, it's no ubber cash but imo better than trying to get a HG group or even solo these guys - it's pure anarchy (<br>
<br>
Silas Silfren<br>
